comments: Andrea is amazing! She will seriously bring out anybody\'s inner artist even if you\'ve never done art before. She gives you great insight on improvement with enthusiasm for your personal tastes. She is optimistic, challenges you, and is an overall eloquent instructor. I love her and recommend her to all my artist colleagues.

Great class! She is a great artist and teacher! She is honest on what tips to give you to improve as an artist. She cares a lot about the students and even emails you if you missed a class. Just turn in your homwork on time and try your best!
Andrea is a wonderful teacher. Helpful, patient and enthusiastic, she is a joy to learn from.
Andrea brings a lot of enthusasism, experience, and energy to the art class. She could be a little more critical of our work, but she gets a lot more out of us than some other art teachers.
